AUDIO: 'Today we are taking a look at Gracia, the 4D GS, that\'s Gaussian Splat Viewer. You may have heard of Gaussian Splat, it\'s a way to take a 2D image, turn into 3D using points. So, the pixels are almost like points in 3D space. These guys have taken it a step further and'

